{"tid":1119551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"放寛海外醫生來港　連病人醫委都投反對（其實政府醫委都投反對）","createTime":"2019-04-22T04:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T04:28:11.000Z","uid":47714,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b7ae1414d991e1dde127ed6e1c6bfd42b3bae951","tid":1119551,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T04:10:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10157309868276579&amp;set=a.10150324932406579&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10157309868276579%26set%3Da.10150324932406579%26type%3D3&d=1KnBewcMxCifpJVTRQbR6ogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=fa22f46e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10157309868276579&amp;set=a.10150324932406579&amp;type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n醫委會呢，32個委員𥚃面，有12個係特首委任嘅，另有3個係病人組織代表，再加1個消委會代表。呢班人加埋，已經佔左醫委會一半。<br />\n<br />\n宜家否決左「豁免實習」全部四個方案，而其中最大比數否決嘅仲包括「方案三：以有限度註冊在醫管局服務，3年內考獲執業資格試，可免實習」。<br />\n<br />\n呢個方案，得3票支持。係3票，3票咋！<br />\n<br />\n即係連政府委員都大部份反對。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/posts/2359207800785606\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup%2Fposts%2F2359207800785606&d=1KnBewcMxCifpJVTRQbR6ogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=b3c32298\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/posts/2359207800785606</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190405/59455015\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190405%2F59455015&d=1KnBewcMxCifpJVTRQbR6ogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=0576c540\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190405%2F59455015&h=619bd53b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190405/59455015</a><br />\n<br 